Author: luplum
Text: Oh man. I feel so puffy today, the cheeks but especially around my eyes, that I could barely stand to look people in the eye at work. It's almost 6 pm and it's only barely gone down since I slept. I've also "gained" like 1,5 kilos and feel super bloated and haven't really registered much hunger all day. Next time I tell myself "Just eat whatever today, it's been a social and foody weekend already and tomorrow is a fresh beginning" I'm gonna remind myself of this feeling.
